 3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; HOW AN AUCTION WORKS</span><br><span style="font-size:12px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">
 A person looking to have solar panels installed on their roof or property
 (the &quot;Roof Owner&quot;) will create an auction by filling out their address,
 roof details, expected terms for installation, and expiry date for the 
auction and then submitting the auction for bids. &nbsp;Once an auction is 
submitted for bids, Users looking to install solar on a Roof Owner&#39;s 
property (the &quot;Solar Installer&quot;) can place a bid on the auction before 
the auction expiry date. Solar Installers post bids by filling out the 
necessary bid fields including price, technology, warranty and company 
track record, and submitting this to the Roof Owner that created the 
auction. &nbsp;Each Solar Installer will only be able to submit one bid per 
auction, and the submission of a bid will act as confirmation that the 
Solar Installer will be held to the terms contained in the bid if they 
are selected as the winning bid by the Roof Owner that created the 
auction. </span><br><span style="font-size:12px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"></span><br><span style="font-size:12px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; BIDDING PROCESS</span><br><span style="font-size:12px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">4.1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The Company has the right to disclose information submitted by the User to the auction owner;</span><br><span style="font-size:12px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"> </span><br><span style="font-size:12px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">4.2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The Company is not the agent or representative of the User and the User is soley responsible for its bid;</span><br><span style="font-size:12px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"> </span><br><span style="font-size:12px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">4.3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
