<span style="font-size:12px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">
4.4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The Company does not guarantee that the User will be succesful, or if succesful that the installation will be completed.</span><br>
<span style="font-size:12px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;"></span><br><span style="font-size:12px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ACCEPTANCE OF THE WIN AND PAYMENT</span><br><span style="font-size:12px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">
After an auction has passed its expiry date, the Roof Owner that created the 
auction will have 10 days to select a winning bid. &nbsp;The Solar Installer 
that submitted this winning bid (the "Winner") will receive an email 
notification with contact information for the Roof Owner and the Winner&#39;s credit card will be automatically charged $100 per kW installation size included in the Winner&#39;s bid (the 
&quot;Gridbid Fee&quot;). If the Winner and Roof Owner decide not to move forward 
with the installation within 30 days, the Company will refund 100% of 
the Gridbid Fee to the Winner</span>
<span style="font-size:12px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:italic;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">. </span>
<span style="font-size:12px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;">
The Winner will be required to contact the Roof Owner within 5 business 
